                <h2>QUESTIONS</h2>
                <!---->
                <h2><small>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Would I be able to recharge my connection while abroad?</small></h2>
                <h2><small>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Will Scratch Cards be available at IR destinations?</small></h2>
