                <p>
                    11.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;How to contact Warid while roaming abroad?
                    If you encounter any difficulties while you are abroad, you can call Warid Contact Center on +92 42 111 111 321. Calls will be charged at the international rate. Or you can write to us at customerservice@waridtel.com
